{
  "id": "6202c83d971cf4001dc3f6dc",
  "title": "CSSセレクタの優先順位",
  "created": 1644349503,
  "updated": 1773577873,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6202c83d971cf4001dc3f6dc",
      "text": "CSSセレクタの優先順位",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644349503,
      "updated": 1644349503
    },
    {
      "id": "6202c8497838e300008a4beb",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/dfb1f9e8506a2c80026e1d676084933d]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644349513,
      "updated": 1644354099
    },
    {
      "id": "6202cac47838e300008a4bf8",
      "text": "\t[https://specifishity.com/ Specifishity :: Specificity with Fish]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644350148,
      "updated": 1644354101
    },
    {
      "id": "62aea8b87838e30000e0df49",
      "text": "\t[CSS Specifishity]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1655613627,
      "updated": 1655613657
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d37f7838e300008a4c03",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352384,
      "updated": 1644352384
    },
    {
      "id": "62fa333e7838e300003c7644",
      "text": "#CSSセレクター",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1660564285,
      "updated": 1660564293
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d3397838e300008a4bff",
      "text": "[https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/Cascade_and_inheritance#specificity_2 カスケードと継承 - ウェブ開発を学ぶ | MDN]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352313,
      "updated": 1644352315
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d2cc7838e300008a4bfc",
      "text": "[詳細度]という値によってセレクタの優先順位が決まる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352205,
      "updated": 1773566369
    },
    {
      "id": "69b679990000000000d2f874",
      "text": "\t[詳細度 - CSS | MDN https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Guides/Cascade/Specificity]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566361,
      "updated": 1773566369
    },
    {
      "id": "69b6795f0000000000d2f871",
      "text": "\t詳細度には（基本的には）3つの列があり、`x-y-z`という形で表記される",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566303,
      "updated": 1773567975
    },
    {
      "id": "69b679db0000000000d2f876",
      "text": "\t左側の列の方が優先度が高く（重みが強く）、右側の列の方が優先度が低い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566426,
      "updated": 1773567912
    },
    {
      "id": "69b679740000000000d2f872",
      "text": "\tそれぞれの列は左から順に以下の通り",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566324,
      "updated": 1773567909
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67a0a0000000000d2f877",
      "text": "\t\tID列",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566474,
      "updated": 1773566476
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67a1a0000000000d2f87a",
      "text": "\t\t\t[IDセレクター]が該当",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566490,
      "updated": 1773566501
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67a0c0000000000d2f878",
      "text": "\t\tCLASS列",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566476,
      "updated": 1773566479
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67a270000000000d2f87b",
      "text": "\t\t\t[クラスセレクター]や[属性セレクター]や[擬似クラスセレクター]が該当",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566503,
      "updated": 1773566544
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67a100000000000d2f879",
      "text": "\t\tTYPE列",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566479,
      "updated": 1773566487
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67a370000000000d2f87c",
      "text": "\t\t\t[要素型セレクター]や[擬似要素セレクター]が該当",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566519,
      "updated": 1773566558
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67a650000000000d2f87d",
      "text": "\t例外として以下のセレクターは詳細度にカウントされない（0-0-0 になる）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566564,
      "updated": 1773567945
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67a750000000000d2f87e",
      "text": "\t\t`*`（[全称セレクター]）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566580,
      "updated": 1773566612
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67a7e0000000000d2f880",
      "text": "\t\t[:where()]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566590,
      "updated": 1773566617
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67a9f0000000000d2f881",
      "text": "\t\t\t[:is()]との違いはまさに詳細度があるかないか",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566623,
      "updated": 1773566640
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67ab10000000000d2f882",
      "text": "\t\t\t詳細は個別ページを参照",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566641,
      "updated": 1773566649
    },
    {
      "id": "69b680360000000000d2f8ce",
      "text": "\t[style属性]（[インラインスタイル]）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773568054,
      "updated": 1773568229
    },
    {
      "id": "69b6803e0000000000d2f8cf",
      "text": "\t\t`<div style=\"<スタイル>\">`のように書いたスタイルはセレクターを指定したスタイルより常に優先される",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773568062,
      "updated": 1773568223
    },
    {
      "id": "69b680bb0000000000d2f8d3",
      "text": "\t\t詳細度は便宜上`s-x-y-z`（sがstyle属性）のような形式で表現されることがある",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773568187,
      "updated": 1773568246
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67b940000000000d2f88e",
      "text": "\t[!important]はそれがついていないプロパティ全てより優先される",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566868,
      "updated": 1773566899
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67bc10000000000d2f88f",
      "text": "\t\tこちらも詳細は個別ページを参照",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566913,
      "updated": 1773566918
    },
    {
      "id": "69b6813b0000000000d2f8d5",
      "text": "\t\tインラインスタイル含め[!important]がついていない全てに対し優先される",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773568315,
      "updated": 1773568338
    },
    {
      "id": "69b680fa0000000000d2f8d4",
      "text": "\t\t詳細度は便宜上`i-s-x-y-z`（iが[!important]）のような形式で表現されることがある",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773568250,
      "updated": 1773568276
    },
    {
      "id": "69b679a30000000000d2f875",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566371,
      "updated": 1773566371
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67c440000000000d2f899",
      "text": "計算された詳細度の確認方法",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567044,
      "updated": 1773567068
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67c4a0000000000d2f89b",
      "text": "\t[Chrome DevTools]の様なブラウザの開発者ツールで確認可能",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567049,
      "updated": 1773567072
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67c600000000000d2f89c",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/801c32b6899914f4bf4114a49f14665c]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567072,
      "updated": 1773567073
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67c610000000000d2f89d",
      "text": "\t\tChromeの場合はセレクターにマウスホバーすることで表示される",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567073,
      "updated": 1773567100
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67c7d0000000000d2f89e",
      "text": "\t\t特異性と表記されているが意味は同じ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567101,
      "updated": 1773567109
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67c440000000000d2f89a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567044,
      "updated": 1773567044
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d3957838e300008a4c04",
      "text": "詳細度は各列での加点制",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352405,
      "updated": 1773567899
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d3be7838e300008a4c05",
      "text": "\t0-0-1",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352446,
      "updated": 1773567439
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d3c17838e300008a4c06",
      "text": "\t\t要素セレクタ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352449,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d3ce7838e300008a4c07",
      "text": "\t\t\t例) `<div id=\"foo\">`に対応する`div`",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352462,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d3f47838e300008a4c08",
      "text": "\t\t擬似要素",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352500,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d42d7838e300008a4c09",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-elements 擬似要素 - CSS: カスケーディングスタイルシート | MDN]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352557,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d4327838e300008a4c0a",
      "text": " 0-1-0",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352562,
      "updated": 1773567435
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d4c37838e300008a4c0b",
      "text": " \t[クラスセレクター]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352707,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d4d07838e300008a4c0c",
      "text": " \t\t例) `<div class=\"foo\">`に対応する`.foo`",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352720,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d4df7838e300008a4c0d",
      "text": " \t[属性セレクター]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352735,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d4ea7838e300008a4c0e",
      "text": " \t\t例) `[href^=\"https://scrapbox.io]`",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352747,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d5237838e300008a4c0f",
      "text": " \t[擬似クラス]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352803,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d5387838e300008a4c10",
      "text": " \t\t例) `:after`",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352824,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d5457838e300008a4c11",
      "text": " 1-0-0",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352838,
      "updated": 1773567434
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d54d7838e300008a4c12",
      "text": " \t[IDセレクター]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352846,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d5527838e300008a4c13",
      "text": " \t\t例) `<div id=\"foo\">`に対応する`#foo`",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352850,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67c080000000000d2f897",
      "text": " 0-10-0",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566984,
      "updated": 1773567433
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67c0d0000000000d2f898",
      "text": " \t例)",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773566988,
      "updated": 1773567143
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67ca70000000000d2f89f",
      "text": " \t\tcode:0-10-0.css",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567143,
      "updated": 1773567149
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67cae0000000000d2f8a0",
      "text": " \t\t\t.foo.foo.foo.foo.foo.foo.foo.foo.foo.foo {",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567149,
      "updated": 1773567153
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67cb20000000000d2f8a1",
      "text": " \t\t\t    /* 0-10-0 のセレクター */",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567154,
      "updated": 1773567166
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67cb20000000000d2f8a2",
      "text": " \t\t\t}",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567154,
      "updated": 1773567154
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67cc40000000000d2f8a3",
      "text": "\t\t同じセレクターを連続させても加算させることができる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567172,
      "updated": 1773567278
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67cef0000000000d2f8a4",
      "text": "\t\tただし、いくら増やしても繰り上がって`1-0-0`のようにはならない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567214,
      "updated": 1773567278
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67d1e0000000000d2f8a5",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/219becdaffa1f13c4928e4168884b4f5]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567261,
      "updated": 1773567278
    },
    {
      "id": "69b6a68a0000000000a45355",
      "text": "\t\t [特異性]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1773577866,
      "updated": 1773577873
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d56f7838e300008a4c14",
      "text": " 1-0-0-0",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352879,
      "updated": 1773567431
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d5757838e300008a4c15",
      "text": " \thtmlの[style属性]（インラインスタイル）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352885,
      "updated": 1773567507
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d57e7838e300008a4c16",
      "text": " \t\t例) `<div style=\"color: black\">`",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352895,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67de30000000000d2f8a7",
      "text": " \tID列より優先される",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567458,
      "updated": 1773567471
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d67d7838e300008a4c18",
      "text": " 1-0-0-0-0",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644353150,
      "updated": 1773567449
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d6807838e300008a4c19",
      "text": " \t[!important]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644353153,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67df40000000000d2f8a8",
      "text": " \t[style属性]より優先される",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567476,
      "updated": 1773567495
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67dfd0000000000d2f8a9",
      "text": " \tCSSファイルや[<style>]のスタイルが[style属性]に勝つには、[!important]に頼る以外に方法はない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773567485,
      "updated": 1773567561
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d7a07838e300008a4c28",
      "text": "\t点数に関係しないもの",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644353440,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d7a77838e300008a4c29",
      "text": "\t\tCSSの結合子",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644353447,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d7ee7838e300008a4c2a",
      "text": "\t\t\t例) `div > a`の`>`",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644353518,
      "updated": 1773566375
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d6347838e300008a4c17",
      "text": " 同じ詳細度の場合は[[後に記述されたセレクタが優先]]される",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644353076,
      "updated": 1773566387
    },
    {
      "id": "66d0456671b3c2000041fe5a",
      "text": "  そのためCosenseの場合app.css < projectcss < usercssの順番で優先される",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1724925286,
      "updated": 1724925309
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d31d7838e300008a4bfe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644352286,
      "updated": 1644352286
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d6ab7838e300008a4c1a",
      "text": "詳細度の例",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644353196,
      "updated": 1644353205
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d6b57838e300008a4c1c",
      "text": "\t0-0-1",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644353205,
      "updated": 1773567574
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d6c07838e300008a4c1d",
      "text": "\t\tcode:1.css",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644353217,
      "updated": 1644353243
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d6c97838e300008a4c1e",
      "text": "\t\t div {}",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1644353225,
      "updated": 1644353236
    },
    {
      "id": "6202d6de7838e300008a4c1f",
      "text": "\t0-0-2",
